Class GameWorld

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.GameWorld

  • public class GameWorld
extends java.lang.Object
    Delegate class used to represent all the current components of the game world.

    Started out as a lightweight model but soon became a monolith...

    Author:
    Marcel van Workum - 300313949, Divya Patel - 300304450, Reuben Puketapu - 300310939, Ellie Coyle - 300307071
